import React from 'react'
import TextInput from '../../components/ui/TextInput'
import useFormContext from '../../Hooks/useFormContext'

const BasicInfo = () => {
  const { userData, handleChange } = useFormContext

  return (
    <TextInput
    fieldName = "firstName"
        placeholder
        pattern
        fieldValue
        handleChange
        disabled/>
  )
}

export default BasicInfo
